<SYNC Start=1880500><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1881098><P Class=KRCC>
5, 6 -- 좋아
<SYNC Start=1883700><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1896196><P Class=KRCC>
금방 돌아올게
